                                jcr:lastModifiedBy="kokajx"
                                jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                text="&lt;p>Since day one our inclusive culture has been the secret to our success. It's reflected in everything we do and everything we offer.&amp;nbsp; At the foundation are the Ways We Work, five pillars that guide how people work, innovate, collaborate and treat one another. It’s what enables individuals, teams and our company as a whole to make a real difference in people’s lives worldwide.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
